title: Bobby’s Friend’s Crazy NASA Sleep Study + Show Member Admits To Secret Credit Card + Bobby Feud: Best Things American’s Have Given The World
itunes:title: Bobby’s Friend’s Crazy NASA Sleep Study + Show Member Admits To Secret Credit Card + Bobby Feud: Best Things American’s Have Given The World
description:
Bobby’s friend Jason calls in to tell us about the crazy NASA sleep study he took part in where he laid in bed for two months to make $7000. Bobby shared a story about most people having had one credit card that their significant other didn't know about…and turns out that rang true for one of our show members. Plus, we play a round of the 'Bobby Feud'...talking about the best things Americans have given the world!
